AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:00:41.662 --> 00:00:42.870
FRANK SCHILBACH: Why is that?

00:00:42.870 --> 00:00:45.810
AUDIENCE: Because
we [INAUDIBLE]..

00:00:49.012 --> 00:00:49.970
FRANK SCHILBACH: Right.

00:00:49.970 --> 00:00:53.317
But I guess one condition
that we have in the commitment

00:00:53.317 --> 00:00:55.650
device-- and that's more like
a question of definition--

00:00:55.650 --> 00:01:00.350
is like it's chosen by the agent
to actually engage in this,

00:01:00.350 --> 00:01:02.070
and I guess you don't
