AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE] the
one with the [INAUDIBLE]..

00:09:44.588 --> 00:09:45.880
FRANK SCHILBACH: Yeah, exactly.

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:47.600
So let me just
repeat what you said.

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:50.200
So you said, people think they
