00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:06.150
We cannot rule this out.

00:11:06.150 --> 00:11:08.310
Now, there's other issues
with like substitution

00:11:08.310 --> 00:11:12.360
to other cards and so on,
so you might sort of--

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:14.160
that might backfire
in various other ways,

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:18.090
